en-shirk\/","url_meta":{"origin":24371,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Omens: Following omens an act of idolatry","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 3, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever turns back from something due to seeing an omen, he has committed idolatry.\u201d They said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, what is the expiation for that?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cThat he says: O Allah, there\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3156,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/05\/09\/swearing-oath-shirk\/","url_meta":{"origin":24371,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Oaths: Swearing by other than Allah an act of idolatry","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 9, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever swears by other than Allah has committed an act of idolatry.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 3251 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Albani Ibn Abi al-'Izz said, \"If one's swearing by other than Allah is intended to adjure\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33524,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/09\/16\/good-luck-charms-idolatry\/","url_meta":{"origin":24371,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Amulets: Wearing good luck charms an act of idolatry","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 16, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Uqbah ibn \u2018Amir reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, received a group of men and he accepted the pledge of nine of them, while he refrained from one. They said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, you accepted the pledge of nine men and left this one\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":20524,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/03\/31\/charms-amulets-magic-sihr\/","url_meta":{"origin":24371,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Charms: Whoever wears an amulet is entrusted to it","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 31, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever ties a knot and blows on it has performed magic, and whoever performs magic has committed idolatry. Whoever hangs something as a charm will be entrusted to it.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Nasa\u0304'i\u0304 4079 Grade: Hasan (fair)\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2932,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/04\/18\/shirk-abandon-mushrikin-idols\/","url_meta":{"origin":24371,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Shirk: Allah abandons idolaters to their idols","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 18, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAllah Almighty said: Verily, I am free of the idolatry of any partners. Whoever performs a deed in which he associates another with Me, I will abandon him to his partner.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2985 Grade:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28991,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/05\/09\/allah-expose-riya-shirk-asghar\/","url_meta":{"origin":24371,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Hypocrisy: Allah will expose hypocrites on Judgment Day","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 9, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Jundub reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever acts to be heard, Allah will make him heard. Whoever acts to show off, Allah will show him off. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6499, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2987 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/24371","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp